    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the national security thing, but isn't it kind of a stretch to call tariffs \"strategic\" when they mostly just subsidize inefficient companies and make life harder for regular people? feels like the \"free trade\" side is just the actual economic truth and everyone else is just playing politics.",
